      • evaluate

        void evaluate(org.qcri.rheem.java.channels.ChannelExecutor[] inputs,
              org.qcri.rheem.java.channels.ChannelExecutor[] outputs,
              org.qcri.rheem.java.compiler.FunctionCompiler compiler)
        Evaluates this operator. Takes a set of Java Streams according to the operator inputs and produces a set of Streams according to the operator outputs -- unless the operator is a sink, then it triggers execution.
        Parameters:
        inputs - ChannelExecutors that satisfy the inputs of this operator
        inputs - ChannelExecutors that collect the outputs of this operator
